payment.alipay_guide_html:
1、Login to Alipay Open Platform<a class='text-[#5A6D9E]' href='https://open.alipay.com/module/webApp/' target='_blank'>https://open.alipay.com/module/webApp/</a>Create "Web/Mobile Application" to get APPID; 
2、Click to enter the application, configure according to the official guide of Alipay in "Development Settings" "Interface Signing Method" to get application private key and Alipay public key; 
3、In "Development Settings" "Authorization Callback Address", fill in: <span  style="color: #FA5151;">{callback_url}</span><span class='copy-hook'></span>
4、In [API Management], access the capability of "PC Website Payment" and configure or activate it according to Alipay's official guidance;

fastgpt_agent_get_tip:
Go to FastGPT ({ url })
 Step 1: Login FastGPT, click "Workbench" then click to select the application to access   
 Step 2: Enter the application and select "API Access" under [Publishing Channels] 
 Step 3: Under API Key Management, click New. After successful creation, copy "API KEY" and fill it into the form; 
Step 4: Copy "API Root Address" and fill it into the form;

maxkb_agent_get_tip:
Go to MaxKB({ url })
 Step 1: Download MaxKB client; 
 Step 2: Click the application to be accessed in "Application"; 
 Step 3: Under "API Access Credentials", copy the Base URL, create and copy the API Key, and fill them into the following form.
